Omaha.KVNO: Classical 90.7 KVNO analog and 90.7 HD 1 is a radio station broadcast at 8,900 watts from the heart of the University of Nebraska at Omaha (UNO) campus. KVNO's broadcasting license is held by the University of Nebraska Board of Regents. The station is a media operations unit of UNO's College of Communication, Fine Arts and Media.
